{"tid":1783113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"痴線！有手足花時間搞咗呢壇嘢","createTime":"2019-12-14T13:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:23:50.000Z","uid":192699,"like":442,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"17a9b7517d526846b6daf7fbc629943dcb47dc95","tid":1783113,"uid":192699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"眼見近日少咗流水式抗爭，但唔代表場運動完咗<br />\n國際戰線仍然如火如荼，而本地嘅黃色經濟圈支線都要搞大佢<br />\n唔好放軟手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色飲食圈就搞得有聲有色，但其他層面都好需要大家去建立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加上現有嘅Page主要係清單咁列出附近有咩黃店<br />\n好多時都唔知佢會唔會仲有咩優惠同活動幫到手足<br />\n結果大家到最後都係集中懲罰一兩間出名嘅黃店<br />\n<br />\n最近有班手足開咗個資訊Page「良介」<br />\n集中處理同整合唔同舖頭嘅優惠、義賣活動等等<br />\n入面除咗飲食，仲會介紹同跟進唔同種類嘅店舖<br />\n等大家有多個選擇，諗清楚先洗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每個層面大家都可以出多一分力，除咗街頭抗爭<br />\n經濟戰線都要下定決心一齊做<br />\n就算休息都要將抗爭精神融入日常生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n良介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ConscienceShare/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FConscienceShare%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=faaa0c1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ConscienceShare/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qXpRLT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qXpRLT.jpg&h=6cb9daf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好放棄，呢條路並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"24b5bba1c8670fa2e8f87aca918c823b0e94af30","tid":1783113,"uid":166149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n推<br />\n已LIKE"},{"pid":"d5d18772fc619d137a52245576bc3f4da62af786","tid":1783113,"uid":307619,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"聽日有社福集會阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpk64Ys.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqpk64Ys.jpg&h=9c03902a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecc62397e2159056695661465a86ee601a0970e8","tid":1783113,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:58:13.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"478243d52337178506fe3f26c3656a9a00c7c9bd","tid":1783113,"uid":192699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:03:06.000Z","msg":"主線、支線大家一齊做<br />\n永遠唔孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79f9ff0d83073e672fec39a308ef3f43ee84c627","tid":1783113,"uid":251769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pDiMkCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpDiMkCu.jpg&h=406aa160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSrVdXx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSrVdXx.jpg&h=a557c3ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e111dd2a7b68df1b5ffae71b209300cb067